{"tid":1827280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《行動》紅磡和你跑今晚9點","createTime":"2020-01-16T23:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T11:56:50.000Z","uid":242262,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"091099f3c5653cdb093708a29927c227258a6b57","tid":1827280,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T23:57:29.000Z","msg":"主題: 齊上齊落, 不離不棄👭👬<br />\n日期: 17 Jan 2020 (Fri) <br />\n集合時間: 🕘21:00 <br />\n<br />\n2nd 集合地點:<br />\n紅磡碼頭 (至終點嘅路程:2.9km)<br />\n<br />\n路線: 紅磡海濱➡️尖沙咀鐘樓<br />\n<br />\n注意事項:<br />\n2) 由於可能會有黎自武漢嘅遊客到訪香港觀賞夜景/混入埋同我地一齊跑, 為預防感染肺炎, 請戴上口罩😷<br />\n4) 請攜帶身份證, 如有需要可帶埋水<br />\n5) 盡量輕便裝, 很抱歉整條路線附近並沒有安全&amp;方便嘅儲物櫃可供借用🙇&zwj;♂🙇&zwj;♀<br />\n8) 當晚21:05後, 將由Pe喺和你跑總谷倒數10聲(純打字),<br />\n10,9,8.......2,1&gt;起跑🏃&zwj;♂🏃&zwj;♀<br />\n9) 星光大道1號小食亭有一間黃店(美樂士多), 可以幫佢打氣同佢講加油, 沿路如果見到外國遊客食野歎茶嘅話。。。。。你要識做呢, 一齊&quot;歡迎&quot;佢地🔊🔊<br />\n11) 17號前&amp;後都會繼續有地區性超級迷你街坊跑團, 請踴躍參與, 練好少少體能, 放走負能量<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uRbZGkt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuRbZGkt.jpg&h=86960037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n7D1UFu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn7D1UFu.jpg&h=a4763520&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eae7b4235fea6237e8bca8065a9eb7ff2a9735bd","tid":1827280,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T00:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abcd640966d280cddeeed578444ae15d1f1baed0","tid":1827280,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T00:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957990f2d6f7d2a9c30f3261c6efe27d90c3383e","tid":1827280,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":